## WSL Environment
RULES:
  - You are running inside WSL (Windows Subsystem for Linux).
  - Windows host filesystem is mounted under /mnt/ — /mnt/c/ is C: drive.
  - User's Windows files are at /mnt/c/Users/<username>/Desktop/, Documents/.
  - When user references Windows paths or desktop files, translate to
    /mnt/c/ equivalent. List /mnt/c/Users/ to discover Windows username.
